     H            Y.
     F** GDIR90 ******************************
     F*  IMPORT ORDER DATA REFORMATION (DIE) *
     F*                K.YASUDA   2000.06.29 *
     F****************************** GDIR90 **
     FGDIPP15 IP  E                    DISK
     FGDIWP90 O   E                    DISK
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80IISKHZ
     I                                        1   40IISKYY
     I                                        5   60IISKMM
     I                                        7   80IISKDD
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80IIODHZ
     I                                        1   40IIODRY
     I                                        5   60IIODRM
     I                                        7   80IIODRD
      *------*
      * PARM *
      *------*
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PHIZK   8
     C                     PARM           PRECD   7
     C                     PARM           PKENS   7
     C                     MOVELPHIZK     @HIZK   80
      *
     C                     ADD  1         WRECD   70
     C           IIODHZ    IFLE @HIZK
     C                     GOTO SKIP
     C                     END
      *
     C                     ADD  1         WKENS   70
     C                     WRITEGDIWP901
      *
     C           SKIP      TAG
      *
     CLR                   MOVE WRECD     PRECD
     CLR                   MOVE WKENS     PKENS
